1152
00:43:45,420 --> 00:43:46,099
Stop fighting over it

1153
00:43:46,519 --> 00:43:47,219
There's work for everyone today

1154
00:43:47,539 --> 00:43:48,099
What is it?

1155
00:43:49,000 --> 00:43:49,500
Slaughtering a pig

